The Zondo Commission has been focusing on money flows this week. JOHANNESBURG - Johannesburg mayor, Geoff Makhubo is expected to testify at the state capture inquiry on Friday morning. Makhubo is been implicated in questionable payments from IT company EOH. READ: State Capture: Zizi Kodwa, Geoff Makhubo implicated The company is alleged to have made payments to several senior ANC members including Makhubu and Zizi Kodwa. Makhubo was the Johannesburg ANC's Treasurer-General and Finance MMC when the payments were made.